data.description: Welcome to this 3 bed, 1 bath, 2 car garage home with dining room, living room and den.  Situated on a corner lot with completely fenced yard.  Some newer windows, insulation, floor coverings, paint, and complete new bath in 2016.  Covered deck of the back with a pavillion great for grilling or outside entertainment.  Lots of attic storage.  Roof 2023, HVAC 2021.
